subject: Hockey, Ice
Olympic Games
lead_paragraph: Rangers goalie Henrik Lundqvist headlined Sweden’s 23-man Olympic roster announced Sunday, but the surprise was the inclusion of Peter Forsberg in Coach Bengt-Ake Gustafsson’s squad.
